330
00:17:51,875 --> 00:17:53,458
Why do I have to
wear this thing.

331
00:17:53,541 --> 00:17:55,166
Cheer up, Kirie.

332
00:17:55,250 --> 00:17:57,250
I think that costume
looks really cute on you.

333
00:17:57,333 --> 00:17:58,583
It could be worse.

334
00:17:58,666 --> 00:18:00,458
