352
00:18:43,291 --> 00:18:45,125
Do or die time, Puny-nari.

353
00:18:45,208 --> 00:18:47,333
We'll play it safe
and knock Kirie out

354
00:18:47,416 --> 00:18:48,666
right away with a Tenho.

355
00:18:48,750 --> 00:18:50,000
What's a Tenho?

356
00:18:50,083 --> 00:18:51,166
Wait, don't tell me.

357
00:18:51,250 --> 00:18:54,291
I've had enough.
I'm done playing.

358
00:18:55,791 --> 00:18:58,875
You sure about that?

359
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,083
The idea behind
Tenho is simple.

360
00:19:03,166 --> 00:19:06,041
